{"tid":2423251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Pit Bull=垃圾狗] [慎入] 3歲女童被鬥牛犬咬傷臉部縫15針　爸爸怒轟狗主不制止：她轉身就走","createTime":"2021-02-25T21:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T09:04:45.000Z","uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ec6c6a8ea7a47221a3b1273089ca5c93c996e1b4","tid":2423251,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T21:36:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2886173\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2886173&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd6wNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=8f182922\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2886173</a><br />\n美國早前發生恐怖意外，一名3歲女童與父母在餐廳排隊點餐時，被另一位顧客的鬥牛犬咬傷，面部需縫15針。狗主目睹意外過程，卻沒有即時阻止，隨後更不顧而去，令女童父母大感錯愕。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.image.cx/qTgQN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.image.cx%2FqTgQN.jpg&h=07469780&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咬傷人的鬥牛犬<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.image.cx/qTdXG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.image.cx%2FqTdXG.jpg&h=5f9d81f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女童在發生意外前的模樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.image.cx/qTxsM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.image.cx%2FqTxsM.jpg&h=f36be023&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">慎看</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://i.image.cx/qTMbt.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.image.cx%2FqTMbt.png&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd6wNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=e1a18d6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.image.cx/qTMbt.png</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://i.image.cx/qToug.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.image.cx%2FqToug.jpg&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd6wNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=e48ec5cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.image.cx/qToug.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://i.image.cx/qT7K3.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.image.cx%2FqT7K3.jpg&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd6wNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=657738e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.image.cx/qT7K3.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報道，3歲女童Ronin Waldroup上月和父母到餐廳排隊點餐，突然一隻鬥牛犬衝到她身旁，撕咬着她的臉。目擊者指，鬥牛犬緊咬女童的臉，並左右搖晃，主人過了一會才把狗狗從女童身上拉下來。意外發生後，狗主若無其事地走開，女童父親追上她，阻止她離開餐廳，<br />\n<br />\n&quot;我女兒臉上都是血，你轉身離開？&quot;<br />\n<br />\n狗主聽後仍然堅持登車離去，令女童父母大感錯愕。女童被送往醫院救治，面部縫了15針。女童在意外後傷心地跟媽媽說，自己變得很醜，令媽媽感到心酸。媽媽指Ronin需要接受整形手術，來掩蓋疤痕。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方及後追查事件，發現鬥牛犬的主人是46歲的Jennifer Romano，根據法庭檔案顯示，他飼養的鬥牛犬Kingston在過去一年內咬傷了兩個人。鬥牛犬隨後被拘留在動物收養中心，並在上月實施安樂死，狗主則被控傷害兒童罪及篡改物證罪。<br />\n<br />\n意外發生後，Ronin家人發起眾籌，冀為女兒籌得醫療費用。"},{"pid":"bc39bbb8a5d5627087c3fc649db9e5e9a83dc1db","tid":2423251,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T22:10:24.000Z","msg":"咪撚俾人養啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d3bfe270b9a621d0d8933ac273387d9364d125d","tid":2423251,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T22:16:00.000Z","msg":"已毀容，所以話美國好快玩完，同中國冇撚分別，多仆街又多左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5edc25b84a202a0fefbff01c3239b3d15fe05a0b","tid":2423251,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc39bbb8a5d5627087c3fc649db9e5e9a83dc1db","tid":2423251,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T22:10:24.000Z","msg":"咪撚俾人養啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T22:17:34.000Z","msg":"UK禁咗三十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8eddc59ce7e56aaa28bd6da9b6394f2e1874d7","tid":2423251,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T22:20:50.000Z","msg":"呢類狗唔係要絕育，應該要絕種<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc65d24d263c774784af01b2051e48f1e4bf404","tid":2423251,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d8eddc59ce7e56aaa28bd6da9b6394f2e1874d7","tid":2423251,"uid":173271,"like":0,